"You are a materials-recommendation normalizer for HVAC/refrigeration service work orders.\nYou will receive a JSON object with a 'suggested_materials' array.\nSuppression has already been applied — do NOT remove any items.\nABSOLUTE RULE — FEES AND RECOVERY CHARGES ARE NEVER REMOVED:\n  The following item types must ALWAYS appear in the output, no exceptions:\n  - Refrigerant recovery fees (e.g. REFRIG RECOVERY(EPA-CAA), REFRIGERANT RECOVERY FEES)\n  - Environmental fees\n  - Disposal charges\n  - Any item whose ITEMDESC contains: recovery, fee, disposal, environmental, charge, EPA\n  These are billable service line items, not physical parts. They are never duplicates\n  of anything and must always pass through exactly unchanged.\nYOUR ONLY JOB:\n  - Generalize every item that has a specific SKU, model number, brand, voltage,\n    refrigerant type, or dimension in ITEMDESC. Rewrite it as a generic description.\n  - Deduplicate: if multiple items belong to the same functional group, collapse\n    them into ONE generic entry using the highest similarity_score.\n  - Pass through items that are already generic (null ITEMNMBR, null CATEGORY,\n    generic ITEMDESC like disposal, hardware, consumables, fees) exactly as-is.\n  - Sort output by similarity_score descending. Ties: ITEMDESC alphabetically ascending.\nGENERALIZATION RULES:\n  - Never copy a specific SKU, part number, model, brand, voltage, or refrigerant type name.\n  - Use these generic ITEMDESC formats:\n      Refrigerant — type and quantity to be confirmed from equipment nameplate\n      Contactor — voltage and amperage to be confirmed from equipment nameplate\n      Filter-Drier — core type and size to be confirmed from equipment specifications\n      Fan Motor — HP, voltage, and RPM to be confirmed from equipment nameplate\n      Capacitor — MFD and voltage to be confirmed from equipment nameplate\n      (follow the same pattern for any other component group)\n  - Set ITEMNMBR to null for all generalized items.\n  - Set CATEGORY to the canonical group name (GAS, CONTACTOR, FILTER-DRIER, MOTOR, etc.)\n  - Set REASONS to: <component> replacement is the primary need; matched <N> variants across similar calls\n  - Set similarity_score to the HIGHEST score among all items collapsed into this group.\nDEDUPLICATION:\n  - One output entry per functional group maximum.\n  - Exception: contactors — one entry per distinct voltage class (e.g. 208V and 120V separately).\n    If voltage is unclear or mixed, collapse all into one entry.\nOUTPUT FORMAT:\n  Output ONLY a valid JSON object. No prose, no markdown, no code fences.\n  First character must be '{', last must be '}'.\n  Schema:\n  {\n    Service_Call_ID: unchanged,\n    search_metadata: unchanged,\n    suggested_materials: [\n      {\n        similarity_score: number,\n        material_details: {\n          ITEMNMBR: null,\n          ITEMDESC: generic description,\n          CATEGORY: group or null,\n          REASONS: one sentence\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n\nHere is the pre-filtered search response to generalize:\n\n{\n  \"Service_Call_ID\": \"250101-0125\",\n  \"search_metadata\": {\n    \"query_vector_source\": \"LK CHECK & EQUIPMENT SURVEY\",\n    \"total_suggestions_found\": 15,\n    \"search_latency_ms\": 27590,\n    \"similar_calls_used\": 50,\n    \"candidates_from_similar_calls\": 82,\n    \"universal_items_injected\": 10\n  },\n  \"suggested_materials\": [\n    {\n      \"similarity_score\": 1,\n      \"material_details\": {\n        \"ITEMNMBR\": null,\n        \"ITEMDESC\": \"CLEAN MATERIALS,RAGS,MISC\",\n        \"CATEGORY\": null,\n        \"REASONS\": \"Used in 32/50 similar calls\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"similarity_score\": 0.2325,\n      \"material_details\": {\n        \"ITEMNMBR\": \"2109\",\n        \"ITEMDESC\": \"CONTACTOR DP 30A 3P 24V COIL OPEN  C25DNF330T\",\n        \"CATEGORY\": \"CONTACTOR\",\n        \"REASONS\": \"Used in 1/50 similar calls\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"similarity_score\": 0.2105,\n      \"material_details\": {\n        \"ITEMNMBR\": \"5587\",\n        \"ITEMDESC\": \"1 GAL TRI POWR COIL CLEANER\",\n        \"CATEGORY\": \"CHEMICAL\",\n        \"REASONS\": \"Used in 1/50 similar calls\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"similarity_score\": 0.2071,\n      \"material_details\": {\n        \"ITEMNMBR\": null,\n        \"ITEMDESC\": \"ELECT CONNECT,TAPE,TIES\",\n        \"CATEGORY\": null,\n        \"REASONS\": \"Standard consumable — used on 26640 service calls\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"similarity_score\": 0.203,\n      \"material_details\": {\n        \"ITEMNMBR\": \"1853\",\n        \"ITEMDESC\": \"CONTACTOR  3P 40A  120V  42CF35AF/C25DNF340A  61446\",\n        \"CATEGORY\": \"CONTACTOR\",\n        \"REASONS\": \"Used in 2/50 similar calls\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"similarity_score\": 0.1923,\n      \"material_details\": {\n        \"ITEMNMBR\": null,\n        \"ITEMDESC\": \"SM DISPOSAL, MTL REMOVED\",\n        \"CATEGORY\": null,\n        \"REASONS\": \"Used in 1/50 similar calls\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"similarity_score\": 0.1876,\n      \"material_details\": {\n        \"ITEMNMBR\": \"3290\",\n        \"ITEMDESC\": \"OIL FILTER CORE SPORLAN OFE-1\",\n        \"CATEGORY\": \"FILTER-DRI\",\n        \"REASONS\": \"Used in 2/50 similar calls\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"similarity_score\": 0.1849,\n      \"material_details\": {\n        \"ITEMNMBR\": \"EZ KLEEN FILTER\",\n        \"ITEMDESC\": \"MESH FILTER\",\n        \"CATEGORY\": null,\n        \"REASONS\": \"Used in 1/50 similar calls\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"similarity_score\": 0.1816,\n      \"material_details\": {\n        \"ITEMNMBR\": null,\n        \"ITEMDESC\": \"ENVIRONMENTAL FEE\",\n        \"CATEGORY\": null,\n        \"REASONS\": \"Standard consumable — used on 14947 service calls\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"similarity_score\": 0.1778,\n      \"material_details\": {\n        \"ITEMNMBR\": null,\n        \"ITEMDESC\": \"BOLTS,SCREWS,BRACING,LUBE\",\n        \"CATEGORY\": null,\n        \"REASONS\": \"Standard consumable — used on 13229 service calls\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"similarity_score\": 0.1679,\n      \"material_details\": {\n        \"ITEMNMBR\": \"6687\",\n        \"ITEMDESC\": \"TEMPRITE STANDARD FILTER KIT FOR 926-927/R - 62028000\",\n        \"CATEGORY\": \"FILTER-OIL\",\n        \"REASONS\": \"Used in 1/50 similar calls\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"similarity_score\": 0.1668,\n      \"material_details\": {\n        \"ITEMNMBR\": \"CONTACTOR\",\n        \"ITEMDESC\": \"Contactor\",\n        \"CATEGORY\": null,\n        \"REASONS\": \"Used in 1/50 similar calls\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"similarity_score\": 0.1661,\n      \"material_details\": {\n        \"ITEMNMBR\": null,\n        \"ITEMDESC\": \"REFRIG RECOVERY(EPA-CAA)\",\n        \"CATEGORY\": null,\n        \"REASONS\": \"Used in 1/50 similar calls\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"similarity_score\": 0.1651,\n      \"material_details\": {\n        \"ITEMNMBR\": \"1806\",\n        \"ITEMDESC\": \"CONTACTOR  3P 40A  208V  42CF35AG/C25DNF340B\",\n        \"CATEGORY\": \"CONTACTOR\",\n        \"REASONS\": \"Used in 1/50 similar calls\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"similarity_score\": 0.1645,\n      \"material_details\": {\n        \"ITEMNMBR\": \"6605\",\n        \"ITEMDESC\": \"REFRIGERANT-R404A-HP62\",\n        \"CATEGORY\": \"GAS\",\n        \"REASONS\": \"Standard consumable — used on 7122 service calls\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}"